Dialog Mission Statement These dialogs are for Vrook Lamar, one of the Jedi Council.
The first dialog is a scripted dialog when the player encounters Vrook for the first time since saving Juhani. The second dialog is a scripted dialog when the player encounters Vrook for the first time since killing Juhani. The third dialog is for subsequent conversations before th player becomes a Padawan. The fourth dialog is after the player has become a Padawan, but before discovering the star map. The fifth dialog is subsequent conversations after the player has been assigned the main quest.
Exit points in conversation:
Exit stream 1: The line is said and the conversation ends. DAN_VROOKJ_DONE is set to TRUE to show that the conversation has taken place.
Exit stream 2: The lines are said and the conversation ends. DAN_VROOKJ_DONE is set to TRUE to show that the conversation has taken place.
Exit stream 3: Th player can ask questions of Vrook but he always says his lines and the conversation ends.
Exit stream 4: The line is said and the conversation ends. DAN_VROOKR_DONE is set to TRUE to show that this conversation has taken place.
Exit stream 5: The lines are said and the conversation ends. DAN_VROOKP_DONE is set to TRUE to show that this conversation has taken place.
